comments: This study reminds me of an alien study for children where they learn an alien language while participating. I noticed that the endings of the shapes varied in their spellings. I wanted to use paper to make some notes and now in retrospect I should have! During the study I felt I wouldn't have enough time but now that I think of it, I had time as the shapes were repeated. I thought Wopicoe was easy to remember but I kept mixing up the other shapes and their spellings!
